videos.description: Tyler King rushes up the middle before bouncing it to the outside to score from 15 yards out, giving the Thundering Herd an early 7-0 lead.
videos.headline: Marshall strikes first as King scampers into end zone

videos.description: Tyler King bursts out of the backfield and leaps over a Middle Tennessee State defender for a 22-yard gain and a first down.
videos.headline: Marshall RB hurdles defender

videos.description: Middle Tennessee State QB John Urzua is pressured in the pocket and has his pass intercepted by Artis Johnson who returns it back 17 yards for a Marshall touchdown.
videos.headline: Thundering Herd defense gets a pick-six

videos.description: One offensive play after throwing a pick-six, the Blue Raiders turn it over again, as the Thundering Herd's Omari Cobb forces a fumble and Chase Hancock recovers.
videos.headline: Marshall forces MTSU fumble

videos.description: Keion Davis takes a handoff and runs through a huge hole up the middle to easily score from nine yards out, giving the Thundering Herd a 21-3 lead.
videos.headline: Davis rushes into end zone untouched for Marshall TD

videos.description: The Blue Raiders cap an 80-yard drive as John Urzua finds Richie James in the end zone for a nine-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Urzua connects with James for MTSU TD

videos.description: Keion Davis powers through the line to score from one yard out, extending the Thundering Herd's lead to 28-10.
videos.headline: Marshall's Davis pounds it in for his 2nd TD of first half

videos.description: John Urzua scrambles away from the pass rush and throws off-balance to connect with Ty Lee for a 49-yard pickup.
videos.headline: MTSU's Urzua escapes pressure, goes deep for huge gain

videos.description: Thundering Herd RB Tyler King breaks several tackles near the line of scrimmage and gets to the sideline for a 28-yard gain and a first down.
videos.headline: Marshall's King showcases his elusiveness on long run

videos.description: On third-and-18, MTSU QB John Urzua completes a short pass to freshman Brad Anderson who cuts upfield and breaks away from multiple defenders to pick up 18 yards and a first down.
videos.headline: Blue Raiders RB spins out of tackle for long third down conversion

videos.description: Injured Middle Tennessee State QB Brent Stockstill says he's aiming to return to the field following the Blue Raiders' bye week.
videos.headline: Stockstill: 'I'm doing everything I can' to return

videos.description: Tyler King's big day continues, scoring from one yard out to give Marshall a 38-10 lead.
videos.headline: Thundering Herd's King reaches end zone for his 2nd TD of game

videos.description: Marshall coach Doc Holliday says it's nice that his team is bowl eligible after a win over MTSU, but says the Thundering Herd's "expectations and standards are a whole lot higher than that."
videos.headline: Holliday pleased with Marshall's execution in win
